23:22.984 --> 23:23.984
And me and Erin.

23:24.152 --> 23:27.321
That's right. Just you and me and Erin.

23:27.489 --> 23:30.157
-Who's Erin?
-Her nanny.

23:30.325 --> 23:32.118
How are you gonna swallow all those?

23:32.285 --> 23:33.661
Have we met?

23:35.288 --> 23:36.997
Erin!

23:50.971 --> 23:52.847
-Good morning, ladies.
-Morning.

23:53.014 --> 23:55.599
