her cartwheels on the lawn.

24:09.739 --> 24:11.240
LILY: Yay.
ERIN: Yay.

24:12.200 --> 24:13.701
CHARLOTTE:
Do you have the sunblock?

24:14.453 --> 24:16.036
ERIN:
Come to me, you little pet.

24:16.204 --> 24:17.538
There you go.

24:17.998 --> 24:21.041
-Yes.
-You have yourselves a lovely morning.

24:21.209 --> 24:23.043
MIRANDA: You too.
CHARLOTTE: Thanks, Erin.

24:23.211 --> 24:26.255
-Oh, that is so sweet.
-I know.

24:27.048 --> 24:28.132
That's your nanny?

24:28.300 --> 24:29.592
Yes, that's Erin.

24:29.759 --> 24:31.260
You mean Erin Go Braless.

24:31.428 --> 24:34.221
Ha, ha. She doesn't wear a bra.

24:34.389 --> 24:37.391
-Was she wearing a bra at the job interview?
