24:58.747 --> 25:00.539
WAITRESS: Are we ready?
MIRANDA: Yes, I think so.

25:00.707 --> 25:01.957
LILY: One, two, three!
HARRY: Yeah, go!

25:03.543 --> 25:08.506
That's a good girl! One more time!

25:15.430 --> 25:20.142
