28:34.337 --> 28:36.171
Yeah.

28:36.881 --> 28:39.133
Mom, you gonna come
to the science fair today?

28:39.300 --> 28:44.138
STEVE: Sorry, honey, she can't. Mommy's--
-She has to go to work. Yeah.

28:47.308 --> 28:51.145
