29:54.209 --> 29:55.209
I never make it.

29:55.376 --> 29:57.044
WOMAN: Good work, Brady.
MAGDA: Good boy.

29:58.087 --> 30:00.756
ERIN:
Your dolphin has got all the skills...

30:00.924 --> 30:03.550
...and it's gonna have a little swim
with the crab.

30:04.219 --> 30:06.261
Yes, it is, baby girl.

30:06.429 --> 30:09.431
Hey, cutie, come look.
Now, what does this do here?

30:09.599 --> 30:11.934
Look at this. Well, what is that gonna do?

30:32.247 --> 30:34.998
There can be many tortured moments
in the life of someone...

30:35.166 --> 30:37.000
