32:50.885 --> 32:53.053
LILY:
Mommy, Mommy.

32:53.221 --> 32:55.097
Mommy.

32:58.393 --> 33:00.769
I was just getting more sprinkles.

33:00.937 --> 33:02.187
Girls.

33:02.355 --> 33:06.191
Let's go and play in my bedroom.

33:06.359 --> 33:08.652
