33:16.744 --> 33:18.578
Good. Come on, darling.

33:19.580 --> 33:21.915
And from no bra
on the Upper East Side...

33:22.083 --> 33:24.042
...to no panties in Times Square.

33:24.210 --> 33:26.378
It's 12 and your lunch is at 12:30.

33:26.546 --> 33:28.088
SAMANTHA:
I'm just freshening up.

33:32.135 --> 33:35.220
Call the restaurant and tell them
I'm going to be 15 minutes late.

33:35.388 --> 33:37.097
MEGHAN:
Samantha Jones.

33:39.976 --> 33:42.436
