34:29.400 --> 34:32.652
Oh. Honey? I gotta go.

34:32.820 --> 34:35.530
I'm pulling up my panties
to get to a lunch date.

34:37.033 --> 34:40.577
[ERYKAH BADU'S "WINDOW SEAT"
PLAYING OVER SPEAKERS]

34:40.745 --> 34:42.161
