34:42.330 --> 34:45.331
...but did I make us
a delicious anniversary meal?

34:45.875 --> 34:47.833
It was delicious.

34:48.002 --> 34:49.668
And you did brag.

34:50.963 --> 34:52.339
Oops.

34:52.507 --> 34:56.009
You have a little osso buco right...

34:57.678 --> 34:59.137
...there.

34:59.305 --> 35:02.682
See, that's one of the perks of eating
at home. You get to kiss the cook.

35:02.850 --> 35:03.850
And no tipping.

35:04.018 --> 35:05.018
[LAUGHING]

35:05.186 --> 35:07.979
